1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,858
And the AI tools meant to help?

2
00:00:01,808 --> 00:00:04,008
They hand you a wall of text and walk away.

3
00:00:04,008 --> 00:00:08,108
You are still the one who has to break the work down, check it, fix it, and stitch it together.

4
00:00:08,108 --> 00:00:09,316
One chatbot.

5
00:00:09,316 --> 00:00:10,633
One generalist.

6
00:00:10,633 --> 00:00:13,325
No plan, and no memory of what it did an hour ago.

7
00:00:13,325 --> 00:00:15,991
You did not get a team — you got another tab to manage.

